NGINX SETUP IN UBUNTU:
----------------------

1: sudo apt update
2: sudo apt install nginx
3: sudo ufw enable 				// if ufw isn't activitated
4: sudo ufw allow 'Nginx HTTP'
5: sudo ufw allow 'OPENSSH' 			// to continueing ssh
6: sudo ufw status
7: systemctl status nginx



BASIC MANAGEMENT COMMANDS:

	sudo systemctl stop nginx
	
	sudo systemctl start nginx
	
	sudo systemctl restart nginx
	
	sudo systemctl reload nginx
	
	sudo systemctl disable nginx
	
	sudo systemctl enable nginx
	

more details: https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-nginx-on-ubuntu-20-04
